# BalanceIQ — Shared Expense Management SaaS

> Transform messy expense spreadsheets into trustworthy, explainable balances.

## Overview

BalanceIQ is a production-grade expense management platform with a key differentiator: a **CSV Import & Anomaly Resolution Engine** that handles messy real-world data and explains every decision. This plan covers a full-stack build with FastAPI + PostgreSQL backend and React + TypeScript frontend.

