### Key Schema Decisions

| Decision | Rationale |
|----------|-----------|
| UUIDs for all PKs | Prevents ID enumeration, safe for distributed systems |
| `join_date` / `leave_date` on `GroupMembers` | Core membership timeline — expenses only apply within active window |
| `csv_row_number` on Expenses/Settlements | Traceability back to original CSV row |
| `import_id` FK on Expenses/Settlements | Links every imported record to its import batch |
| `resolution` + `resolution_data` on Anomalies | Stores user decision with full audit trail |
| Ledger-based balances (no stored balance column) | Balances are always derived, never stale |

